Microsoft Entra Domain Services provides managed domain services such as domain join, group policy, LDAP, and Kerberos without deploying domain controllers.

It is useful for legacy applications requiring traditional directory services.

For example, older enterprise apps can use domain services in Azure.

A real-life use case is lifting legacy workloads to the cloud.

Another example is extending domain capabilities without infrastructure overhead.

Entra Domain Services simplifies domain-based cloud deployments.
